# Spartan Paradigm Requirements Testing //rough outline modify as needed.
## Actors
- Visitor
- Contributor

### Use Cases
#### 1. Contributor: Create/modify provider profile use case:
1. Contributor (C1) logs in for the first time and creates/edits a profile.
#### 2. Contributor: Create/edit a new blog post
2. C1 creates a new blog post (B1) with title = "final_presentation".  
3. C1 edits B1 content.
4. C1 exits the app.

#### 1. Visitor: Create visitor profile:
1. Visitor (V1) logs in for the first time and creates/edits a profile.

#### 2. Visitor:  Browse available blog posts.
2. Visitor V1 searches for available blog B1 (title = "final_presentation").
#### 3. Visitor: React to blog posts.
3. V1 views/likes/comments to B1.
4. (V1 subscribes to S1.)?*

#### 4. Visitor: Apply for posting priviledges.
5. V1 applies for posting priviledges.
6. V1 exits the app.

#### 3. Contributor: View post analytics.
1. C1 logs into the app and views their post stats.
#### 4. Contributor: Reply to comments.
2. C1 replies to V1 comment left on B1.
3. C1 exits the app.
